{
  "text": "The spatial fractional differential operator is also an important tool to describe the anomalous diffusion phenomenon; when 1 < < 2, it represents a L\u00e9vy -stable flight [CITATION_1] ; when \u2192 2, it models a Brownian diffusion process.",
  "correct_citation": {
